    - target: {fileID: 3761541483239895710, guid: dc7360efdc9ea504d9ae1776f72d8632, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'CLUEBOARD: HOW TO USE



        TRANSFER CLUES: Click and drag items
        from your inventory onto the board.



        PLACE CLUES: Drag photos from
        the spawn tray into any empty slot on the board.



        FIND SUSPECTS:
        Explore the game to uncover suspects. They will automatically appear at the
        top of the board once discovered.



        CONNECT THREADS: Click and drag
        a red thread from a Suspect to a Clue to connect them. (Right-click while
        drawing to cancel).



        CUT STRINGS: Left-click any connected Clue
        to remove the connection.



        RETURN ITEMS: Right-click a Clue on
        the board to send it back to your inventory.


        SOLVE THE CASE: To
        decide which suspect is guilty, connect 3 Clues to their photo. Once you
        do, the "Submit Solution" button will turn green. Click it to submit your
        evidence.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4595600416492452890, guid: dc7360efdc9ea504d9ae1776f72d8632, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: ClueboardTutorialCanvas
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8753943928209586438, guid: dc7360efdc9ea504d9ae1776f72d8632, type: 3}
      propertyPath: boardTrigger
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1905876299}
